  <prompt>
    Instrument routing telemetry for the Phase 5 file-aware dispatcher per ADR-015 tier-1 safe rules. Emit App Insights events / metrics for: `(filesCount, filesAllAgree, decidersInvoked, selectedPlaybookId, selectionConfidence, manifestPresent, perFileLatencyMs[], totalLatencyMs)`. Payloads carry tier-1 fields only â€” deterministic IDs, counts, durations, controlled enums. NEVER user message text, file content, query text, reason text.
  </prompt>

  <role>SPAARKE platform observability engineer. Familiar with App Insights custom events + ADR-015 tier-1 hygiene rules.</role>

  <goal>
    Routing telemetry events flow to App Insights from `PlaybookDispatcher`. Each dispatch emits at least one custom event (e.g., `RoutingDispatchCompleted`) with the listed tier-1 dimensions. Verification via App Insights query confirms no content leakage; unit tests assert the event-emission code does not include user message or file content fields.
  </goal>

  <context>
    <background>
      Per spec NFR-A7 + ADR-015 + design Â§1.2 telemetry plan. The telemetry surface enables (a) routing accuracy monitoring, (b) `selectionConfidence` threshold calibration, (c) detection of regressions. Per ADR-015 tier-1: only deterministic identifiers, counts, durations, enums, hashes are allowed in logs. The dispatcher already emits some telemetry (R5SummarizeTelemetry etc.); this task consolidates routing-specific telemetry into a coherent surface.
    </background>
    <relevant-files>
      <file>src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/Chat/PlaybookDispatcher.cs</file>
      <file>src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/Telemetry/</file>
    </relevant-files>
  </context>

  <constraints>
    <constraint source="ADR-015">Tier-1 logging â€” log only IDs, counts, sizes, timings, outcome codes; never content.</constraint>
    <constraint source="NFR-A7">Telemetry/`context.*` events carry tier-1 fields only.</constraint>
    <constraint source="spec FR-18">`decidersInvoked` count must be recorded for case-distribution monitoring.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-029">Per-task BFF publish-size measurement; expect minor delta.</constraint>
  </constraints>

  <knowledge>
    <files>
      <file>projects/spaarke-ai-platform-chat-routing-redesign-r1/spec.md</file>
