    <criterion testable="true">BFF publish-size delta reported.</criterion>
  </acceptance-criteria>

  <notes>
    The negative-sentinel test (step 4) is the strongest ADR-015 hygiene guarantee â€” if any future contributor inadvertently adds user content to the telemetry payload, the test fails. Use cryptographically distinctive sentinels.
  </notes>

